<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/remix/remixicon.css" type="text/css">
</head>
<style>
    .movie-poster{
        display: flex;
    }
    .details{
        /* border: 1px solid black; */
        display: flex;
        height: 500px;
      
    }
    .movie-poster img{
        margin: 30px 0 30px 150px;
        border-radius: 15px;
    }
    .movie-details{
        margin-left: 40px;

        
        margin-top: 80px;
    }
    .movie-vote{
        border: 1px solid black; 
        width: 350px;
        margin: -5px;
        background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);
        color: white;
        font-weight: 500;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

.movie-vote p{
    margin-left: 20px;
    font-size: 18px;
}
.movie-vote a {
    border: 1px solid black;
    margin: 8px;
    padding: 10px 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: black;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
   
}
.movie-details h4{
    background-color: white;
    color: black   ;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
}
.movie-details h4 span:hover{
    border-bottom: 1px solid white;
}
.movie-time{
    display: flex;
    
}
.movie-time h6,.movie-time h5{
    margin-left: 20px;
}
.movie-book a{
    border: 1px solid black;
  padding: 8px 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 20px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: white;
  background-color: rgb(248, 68, 100);
  
}
.movie-book{
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.container{
    background: url('<%= MovieData.Image %>');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    object-fit: cover;
    width: 100%;
    height: 500px;
    background-size: cover;
    
}
.comment-section{
    margin-left: 150px;
}
.comment-show{
border: 1px solid black;
width: 200px;
margin-top:10px ;
border-radius: 10px;
background-color: wheat;
/* box-shadow: 10px 10px 10px  8px #888888; */
 box-shadow: 0 0 6px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); 

}
.comment-show p{
 text-align: center;
 margin: 0;
 padding: 5px 10px;
}
input{
    width: 300px;
    padding: 10px 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

</style>
<body>
    

    <div class="container">
        <div class="details">
            <div class="movie-poster">
                <img src="<%= MovieData.Image %>" width="300px" alt="" c>
            </div>
         <div class="movie-details">
            <h1><%= MovieData.movieName %></h1>
           <div class="movie-vote">
            <p>‚≠ê<%= MovieData.rating %>/10 <span>(387k Votes)</span></p>
            <a href="">Rate Now</a>
           </div>
          <h4><span>2D,3D,ICE,4DX,4DX 3D,IMAX 2D,IMAX 3D</span></h4>
          <h4><%= MovieData.category %></h4>
      <div class="movie-time">
        
        <ul style="display:flex; margin: 0 -30px;">
            <li style="list-style: none;"><%= MovieData.movieTime %></li>
            <li style=" margin-left: 50px;"><%= MovieData.movieTypes %></li>
            <li style=" margin-left: 50px;"><%= MovieData.movieDate %></li>
        </ul>
        
      </div>
      <div class="movie-book">
        <a href="">Book Ticket</a>
      </div>
         </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h3 style="margin-left: 150px;">About the Movie</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.2px;vertical-align: initial; margin:0 300px 0 150px;"><span><%=MovieData.movieName %></span> :  picks up from the explosive events of the first part, following Pushpa`s meteoric rise as he expands his red <br> sandalwood empire beyond borders. As tensions escalate with rival factions and the authorities, his growing ambitions draw <br/> him into intense confrontations and political upheavals.</p>
    </div>

    <form action="/insertcomment" method="post" style="margin-left: 150px; margin-top: 20px;">
        <input type="text" name="comment" placeholder="comment">
       <button  type="submit" style="padding: 10px 15px; border: 10px; background-color: rgb(248, 68, 100); font-size: 15px; color: white; border-radius: 10px;" >submit</button>
    </form>
    
   <div class="comment-section">
    <% commentView.forEach(v => { %>
       
       <div class="comment-show"> <p> <%= v.comment %></p></div>
 
<% }) %>
   </div>
   
</body>
</html>
